<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><Regulation lims:pit-date="2006-03-22" lims:lastAmendedDate="2006-03-22" lims:current-date="2025-07-24" lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="976037" lims:id="976037" regulation-type="SOR" xml:lang="en" xmlns:lims="http://justice.gc.ca/lims"><Identification lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="976038" lims:id="976038"><InstrumentNumber>SOR/95-479</InstrumentNumber><RegistrationDate><Date><YYYY>1995</YYYY><MM>10</MM><DD>3</DD></Date></RegistrationDate><ConsolidationDate lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22"><Date><YYYY>2025</YYYY><MM>7</MM><DD>25</DD></Date></ConsolidationDate><EnablingAuthority lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="976040" lims:id="976040"><XRefExternal reference-type="act" link="N-20.8">DEPARTMENT OF NATURAL RESOURCES ACT</XRefExternal></EnablingAuthority><ShortTitle lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="976041" lims:id="976041">Report on the State of Canada’s Forests Regulations</ShortTitle><LongTitle lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="976042" lims:id="976042">Regulations Respecting the Report on the State of Canada’s Forests</LongTitle><RegulationMakerOrder><RegulationMaker>P.C.</RegulationMaker><OrderNumber>1995-1681</OrderNumber><Date><YYYY>1995</YYYY><MM>10</MM><DD>3</DD></Date></RegulationMakerOrder></Identification><Order lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="976043" lims:id="976043"><Provision lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="976044" lims:id="976044" language-align="yes" format-ref="indent-0-0" list-item="no"><Text>His Excellency the Governor General in Council, on the recommendation of the Minister of Natural Resources, pursuant to section 7 of the Department of <XRefExternal reference-type="act">Natural Resources Act</XRefExternal><FootnoteRef idref="footnote1star_e">*</FootnoteRef>, is pleased hereby to make the annexed Regulations respecting the report on the state of Canada’s forests.</Text><Footnote id="footnote1star_e" placement="page" status="official"><Label>*</Label><Text>S.C. 1994, c. 41</Text></Footnote></Provision></Order><Body lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="976045" lims:id="976045"><Heading lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="976046" lims:id="976046" level="1"><TitleText>Short Title</TitleText></Heading><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:lastAmendedDate="2006-03-22" lims:fid="976047" lims:id="976047"><Label>1</Label><Text>These Regulations may be cited as the <XRefExternal reference-type="regulation" link="SOR-95-479">Report on the State of Canada’s Forests Regulations</XRefExternal>.</Text></Section><Heading lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="976048" lims:id="976048" level="1"><TitleText>Report</TitleText></Heading><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:lastAmendedDate="2006-03-22" lims:fid="976049" lims:id="976049"><Label>2</Label><Text>By June 30 of each year, the Minister of Natural Resources shall prepare a report respecting the state of the forests in Canada and their contribution to the economy and environment of Canada and to the social well-being of Canadians.</Text></Section></Body></Regulation>